-- Pirelli's Gori Says Investment in Plants is Rising, Milano Finanza Reports
-- Chiara Remondini
-- 2010-07-31T10:19:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-31/pirelli-s-gori-says-investment-in-plants-is-rising-milano-finanza-reports.html

          
          
             Pirelli & C SpA , Europe’s third-
largest tiremaker, is increasing investment to add capacity at
its plants,  Francesco Gori , chief executive officer of the tire
unit, was quoted as saying by  Milano Finanza .  
 Pirelli boosted investment by 50 million euros ($65
million) to 350 million euros, Gori said, according to the
newspaper. “Our plants are operating at maximum capacity,” he
was reported as saying.  
